observations.recommendation:
We recommended that the Municipal Mayor:
a. require the Inventory Committee to conduct the physical count of the Road networks and submit the Report on the Physical Count of the Road Network System (RPCLRN);
b. instruct the General Services Officer (GSO) to maintain Local Road Network Property Card (LRNPC) and prepare a Report on Local Road Network (RLRN);
c. request the Municipal Engineer to provide the requested details and cost segregation of road components; and
d. direct the Municipal Accountant to keep and maintain Local Road Network Ledger Card and reconcile the same with the results of physical inventory and to disclose the required supporting information in the Notes to Financial Statements in accordance with COA Circular No. 2015-008.
